                "### 🟡 Average Match Rate\n",
                "\n",
                "**What:** Mean % of correct tool selections across all traces.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Finding:** \\~47% across all models — wrong more than half the time.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Implication:** No high-stakes autonomous deployment without human-in-the-loop."
