                "**What:** % of traces where the agent used *none* of the required tools.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Finding:** \\~52% total failures. Less than 1% show partial success.\n",
                "\n",
                "**Implication:** Bimodal pattern — agents either fully understand or completely miss."
